      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. Garden ¶ 6/3/71 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ In compliance with your instructions I have the honor to submit an estimate of the expenditure, which I would recommend for the service of the botanic Garden ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.03.06a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James McCulloch</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Z71/6820, unit 533, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot. Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">6/3/71</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In compliance with your instructions I have the honor to submit an estimate of the expenditure, which I would recommend for the service of the botanic Garden during the next financial year (from 1 July 1871 til 30 June 1872)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Governments Botanist and Director of the botanic Garden</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£610.- .-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Director is obliged to provide scientific books, journals, instruments, office light, expenses for foreign agencies, many transit expenses abroad, nearly all the means for his conveyance, a horse and many other outlays from his salary, no allowances of any kind having ever been granted. Though in successive years records of quarters to the Director did appear on the estimates, such quarters are not really provided, the building, in which he endeavoured to accommodate himself being entirely required for the departmental service, and thus not even a single private room available to the Director.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; "
                        cols="2">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">2,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>There is no number 1 in the MS.</p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Wages for Gardeners, a travelling collector of plants and seeds, various labourers, an enginedriver, a mechanic, a carter, a messenger, also remuneration for Office assistance, Museum assistance and Laboratory assistance &amp;c.</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£2691.- .-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; "
                        cols="2">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">3, Purchase of Museum material, of plants and seeds</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£130.- .-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; "
                        cols="2">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">4, Victorian Governments contribution towards the publishing fund of the work on Australian plants, issued in London, for the 6th volume</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£100.- .-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; "
                        cols="2">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">5, Stores, timber, bricks, tools, stationery, drain pipes, waterpipes</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£250.- .-<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>250<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">deleted and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>200<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">interlined in an unknown hand</seg>.</p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; "
                        cols="2">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">6, Forage for one cart horse, aviary and waterbirds</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£85.- .-<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>0<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">superimposed over<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>5<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">in an unknown hand.</seg>
                              </p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; "
                        cols="2">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">7, Transit and incidental expenses, including outlays for minor purchases and small repairs</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£120.- .-<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>120<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">deleted and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>140<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>interlined in an unknown hand.</seg>
                              </p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; "
                        cols="2">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">8, Travelling expenses<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£40.- .-<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>8, Travelling expenses £40<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">deleted. The</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">document has been</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>initialled</seg>: 'McC'<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">at this point, probably applying to all the changes marked</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">.</seg>
                              </p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Total</seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border-top: 0.0069in solid #000000; border-left: none; border-bottom: none; border-right: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; "
                        cols="2">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£4026.- .-<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn5" n="6">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The total has been deleted, but no alternative substituted.</p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In comparing this proposed estimate with that of the last 1½<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>years it will be observed, that a saving of £250.-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>is proposed, by abolishing the functions, which the forest Inspector exercised at the bot. Garden during the above period, it being respectfully recommended that the duties of this officer may be restricted to forest work under the hon. the Minister of Lands solely. An addition of £100.- .-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>cannot be avoided in the new estimate under publishing works, the above sum being due since the beginning of the year to the President of the Linnean Society of London, in continuance of an official stipulation entered into some years ago.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I deem it also advisable to bring under the consideration of the ministerial Chief, that my Department should refund henceforth to the Industrial Schools the actual expenditure for the maintenance of the orphan-boys, which the hon. the Chief Secretary may allow to work here also in future, and for this purpose perhaps a rate of payment by the week or month might be fixed.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>It is almost superfluous to remark, that for such payment to the orphan boys a special sum would require to be additionally provided<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn6" n="7">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The final sentence is a marginal addition with its intended position indicated.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be, Sir, your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller, M.D.,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Direct. botan Garden</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honor. the Chief Secretary.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn7" n="8">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>There is an annotation, probably by McCulloch: 'Provide for Inspr of the Forests'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
